  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate techniques for monitoring the course of interstitial therapy for polyomavirus
      nephritis in kidney and kidney pancreas transplant recipients by monitoring blood, urine, and
      renal transplant biopsies of patients affected by polyomavirus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate techniques for monitoring the course of interstitial therapy for polyomavirus
      nephritis in kidney and kidney pancreas transplant recipients by monitoring blood, urine, and
      renal transplant biopsies of patients affected by polyomavirus.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
